      "name": "Maw",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>The demon attacks a target within melee range, aiming to deal 10/W8 and hitting&nbsp;everyone nearby to the target. Only one attack roll needs to be made, but all targets must roll to defend. Those hit must succeed at a TN 6 Prowess saving throw or be swallowed whole. Those that are&nbsp;swallowed take a 7/W6 Wound. Inside the demon, they will take a 4/W4 Wound at the beginning of&nbsp;their respective turns as they are digested. They can cut their way out by dealing at least 8 points of&nbsp;damage in a single attack with a bladed weapon. The demon cannot defend against attacks made&nbsp;from within it, treating it as if it rolled 0 hits to defend.</p>",
        "action": "major"
      },
